\section{What forces a connection}{

Any verb that touches board contents — \code{\link[=gdpins_pin_read]{gdpins_pin_read()}},
\code{\link[=gdpins_pin_write]{gdpins_pin_write()}}, \code{\link[=gdpins_pin_path]{gdpins_pin_path()}}, \code{\link[=gdpins_pin_remove]{gdpins_pin_remove()}},
